\
Gatsby took up his drink.\
\
\'93They certainly look cool,\'94 he said, with visible tension.\
\
We drank in long, greedy swallows.\
\
\'93I read somewhere that the sun\'92s getting hotter every year,\'94 said Tom\
genially. \'93It seems that pretty soon the earth\'92s going to fall into\
