\'93I told you what\'92s been going on,\'94 said Gatsby. \'93Going on for five\
years\'97and you didn\'92t know.\'94\
\
Tom turned to Daisy sharply.\
\
\'93You\'92ve been seeing this fellow for five years?\'94\
\
\'93Not seeing,\'94 said Gatsby. \'93No, we couldn\'92t meet. But both of us loved\
