\
\'93I\'92m not?\'94 Tom opened his eyes wide and laughed. He could afford to\
control himself now. \'93Why\'92s that?\'94\
\
\'93Daisy\'92s leaving you.\'94\
\
\'93Nonsense.\'94\
\
\'93I am, though,\'94 she said with a visible effort.\
\
\'93She\'92s not leaving me!\'94 Tom\'92s words suddenly leaned down over Gatsby.\
\'93Certainly not for a common swindler who\'92d have to steal the ring he\
