\
\'93I won\'92t stand this!\'94 cried Daisy. \'93Oh, please let\'92s get out.\'94\
\
\'93Who are you, anyhow?\'94 broke out Tom. \'93You\'92re one of that bunch that\
hangs around with Meyer Wolfshiem\'97that much I happen to know. I\'92ve\
