\'93You can suit yourself about that, old sport,\'94 said Gatsby steadily.\
\
\'93I found out what your \'91drugstores\'92 were.\'94 He turned to us and spoke\
rapidly. \'93He and this Wolfshiem bought up a lot of side-street\
